{"type": "article", "id": 7408, "title": "MacBook emoji 全表情键盘膜", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-16T07:21:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234433zyBcNT7jH5XAYE0b.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是 Disk Cactus 公司给重度表情爱好者的福利：他们推出了一款 MacBook Emoji 表情键盘膜，允许用户直接从键盘上输入 emoji 表情，目前这套表情有150个，每个表情被单独印刷在键盘上，通过Shift、Control，Option 键可以激活相关的表情。表情和普通输入法之间只需要 “Caps Lock” 便可以自由切换。这款产品适用于 2010 年以后发布的所有 Macbook Pro 和 Air 系列。目前售价 35 美元，正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/diskcactus/the-emoji-keyboard-type-emoji-on-your-mac/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234429Zd7RY5oNijQ9zqc2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344293bdFI8rxMQkUXHqT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234430mxOEHuKf1FStPdYN.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.18142857\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234430O72wvBxlyc0bW4oa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.54264706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}